<div class="phase-desc">Order hsCRP (not standard CRP), homocysteine, and a metabolic panel (fasting glucose, insulin, triglycerides, ALT). Add IL-6 if you want the upstream cytokine picture. This baseline tells you how much work needs to be done and which targets are elevated.</div>
