<div class="phase-desc">Eliminate ultra-processed foods and added sugars. Shift toward a Mediterranean-style eating pattern: olive oil as primary cooking fat, fatty fish 2 to 3 times per week, generous vegetables and legumes, limited refined carbohydrates. Start omega-3 supplementation at 2 to 4g combined EPA+DHA per day. This is the highest-leverage dietary change you can make for hsCRP.</div>
