<div class="phase-desc">Target 7 to 9 hours of consistent sleep. No alcohol within 3 hours of bed. If you snore or wake unrefreshed, consider a sleep study &#8212; untreated sleep apnea is one of the most common reversible inflammatory drivers. Sleep deprivation raises IL-6 by 40 to 60% &#8212; no supplement can compensate for 5 hours of sleep.</div>
