<div class="phase-desc">150+ minutes of moderate-intensity aerobic exercise per week, plus 2 to 3 resistance training sessions. Walking counts &#8212; a 2022 meta-analysis found even low-intensity walking reduced hsCRP significantly. Skeletal muscle contractions release anti-inflammatory myokines (particularly IL-10) that directly counter the pro-inflammatory cytokines from visceral fat. Avoid overtraining &#8212; excessive intensity without recovery raises inflammatory markers acutely.</div>
